      "Negotiation leverage: Ask for discount (almost always get 15-30% off). Leverage: (1) Year-long commitment (get discount vs. monthly), (2) Volume (grow spending with them, renegotiate), (3) Timing (negotiate at renewal, not random month), (4) Competitor (have alternative, mention it). Most vendors build 20-30% discount room into pricing.",
